@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Use this page to detail your site's privacy policy.</p>

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to <strong>Flash</strong>, your trusted destination for renting and purchasing cars with convenience and confidence. At Flash, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a transparent data processing experience.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, billing address, government-issued ID, and payment details.</li>
        <li><strong>Vehicle Preferences:</strong> Rental period, preferred dealerships, insurance preferences.</li>
        <li><strong>Browsing Data:</strong> IP address, device type, interactions, and analytics.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies & Tracking:</strong> Used for personalization and analytics.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Facilitating car rentals and purchases</li>
        <li>Verifying identity and preventing fraud</li>
        <li>Processing payments securely</li>
        <li>Providing customer support</li>
        <li>Sending promotional offers (with consent)</li>
        <li>Improving website functionality</li>
        <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
    <p>We may share your information with third-party payment processors, dealerships, insurance providers, and government authorities when required.</p>

    <h2>Data Security Measures</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> All sensitive data is encrypted to prevent unauthorized access.</li>
        <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Restricted access to personal information, ensuring only authorized personnel can handle user data.</li>
        <li><strong>Regular Audits:</strong> We conduct periodic security audits to identify and mitigate risks.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Retention Policy</h2>
    <p>We retain user data only for as long as necessary to provide our services. Personal information related to transactions is retained in compliance with tax and legal regulations.</p>

    <h2>User Responsibilities</h2>
    <p>As a user, you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account details and ensuring accurate information when using our services.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights & Choices</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Access and update personal information</li>
        <li>Opt-out of marketing emails</li>
        <li>Request data deletion (subject to legal compliance)</li>
        <li>Adjust cookie preferences</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Flash may contain links to third-party services. We encourage reviewing their privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>International Data Transfers</h2>
    <p>For users outside our operating region, your data may be processed in locations where data protection laws differ from your home country. We implement security measures to ensure compliance with international privacy standards.</p>

    <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>Flash does not knowingly collect data from users under 18. Any such data will be deleted.</p>

    <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Continued use of our services indicates acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@flashcars.com">privacy@flashcars.com</a></p>
    <p>Phone: +20 1005299835</p>
    <p>Address: Nile Street 21, Assiut</p>
</div>


